msgstr "Tabblad Composities"

#: ../../compositing/compositions.rst:29
msgid "Make the Compositions widget visible in :menuselection:`Menu --> View --> Compositions`."
msgstr "Maak het widget Composities zichtbaar in :menuselection:`Menu --> Beeld --> Composities`."

#: ../../compositing/compositions.rst:31
